# brew-audit-ignore
#
# Packages listed here are excluded from brew-audit drift detection
# on ALL machines (this file is committed to the dotfiles repo).
#
# For machine-specific ignores, use ~/.brew-audit-ignore-local instead
# (select "skip-local" in brew-audit's triage UI).
#
# Add formula or cask names, one per line.
# Lines starting with # are comments.
